{"title":"数据结构代码实现：二叉树排序树","uid":"60c424b0116ca0c7f0541d6df3017fff","slug":"DataStructure-BST","date":"2020-05-17T01:33:21.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:15.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-BST.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200517093515.png","content":"<h2 id=\"二叉排序树的定义\"><a href=\"#二叉排序树的定义\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二叉排序树的定义\"></a>二叉排序树的定义</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">typedef int KeyType;\ntypedef struct BSTNode&#123;\n    KeyType key;\n    struct BSTNode *lchild,*rchild;\n&#125;BSTNode,*BiTree;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"插入操作\"><a href=\"#插入操作\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"插入操作\"></a>插入操作</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>每次插入从根结点开始，如果要插入的值小于当前结点，则插入其左子树，如果要插入的值大于当前结点，则插入其右子树</p></blockquote>\n<p><img src=\"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200517093529.png\" alt=\"插入操作\"></p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">bool BSTInsert(BiTree &amp;T, KeyType key) &#123;\n    if(NULL&#x3D;&#x3D;T)&#123;\n        T&#x3D;(BiTree)malloc(sizeof(BSTNode));\n        T-&gt;key&#x3D;key;\n        T-&gt;lchild&#x3D;T-&gt;rchild&#x3D;NULL;\n        return true;\n    &#125;else if(key&#x3D;&#x3D;T-&gt;key)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;不插入相同元素，\n        return false;\n    &#125;else if(key&lt;T-&gt;key)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要插入的值小于当前结点，则插入其左子树\n        return BSTInsert(T-&gt;lchild,key);\n    &#125;else&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要插入的值大于当前结点，则插入其右子树\n        return BSTInsert(T-&gt;rchild,key);\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"搜索\"><a href=\"#搜索\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"搜索\"></a>搜索</h2><blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>从根结点开始，如果要搜索的值小于当前结点的值，则继续寻找他的左子树，如果要搜索的值大于当前结点的值，则继续寻找他的右子树，直到找到为止</p></blockquote>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">BSTNode *BSTSearch(BiTree T,KeyType key,BiTree &amp;p)&#123;\n    p&#x3D;NULL;\n    while(T!&#x3D;NULL&amp;&amp;key!&#x3D;T-&gt;key)&#123;\n        p&#x3D;T;\n        if(key&lt;T-&gt;key)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要搜索的值小于当前结点的值，则继续寻找他的左子树\n            T&#x3D;T-&gt;lchild;\n        &#125;else&#123;\n            T&#x3D;T-&gt;rchild;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要搜索的值大于当前结点的值，则继续寻找他的右子树\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n    return T;\n&#125;</code></pre>\n\n<h2 id=\"删除结点\"><a href=\"#删除结点\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"删除结点\"></a>删除结点</h2><ul>\n<li>如果要删除的元素小于当前元素，则查找他的左子树</li>\n<li>如果要删除的元素大于当前元素，则查找他的右子树</li>\n<li>找到了要删除的元素后，如果左子树为空，则将其右子树放在要删除的位置，如果右子树为空，则将其左子树放在要删除的位置，如果都不为空，一般删除策略是左子树的最大数据或者右子树的最小数据代替要删除的结点（这里采用查找左子树最大数据来代替）<pre class=\"line-numbers language-c++\" data-language=\"c++\"><code class=\"language-c++\">void DeleteNode(BiTree &amp;root,KeyType x)&#123;\n    if(root&#x3D;&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n        return;\n    &#125;\n    if(root-&gt;key&gt;x)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要删除的元素小于当前元素，则查找他的左子树\n        DeleteNode(root-&gt;lchild,x);\n    &#125;else if(root-&gt;key&lt;x)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;如果要删除的元素大于当前元素，则查找他的右子树\n        DeleteNode(root-&gt;rchild,x);\n    &#125;else&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;找到了要删除的元素\n        if(root-&gt;lchild&#x3D;&#x3D;NULL)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;左子树为空\n            BiTree tempNode&#x3D;root;\n            root&#x3D;root-&gt;rchild;\n            free(tempNode);\n        &#125;else if(root-&gt;rchild&#x3D;&#x3D;NULL)&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;右子树为空\n            BiTree tempNode&#x3D;root;\n            root&#x3D;root-&gt;lchild;\n            free(tempNode);\n        &#125;else&#123;&#x2F;&#x2F;左右子树都不为空，一般删除策略是左子树的最大数据或者右子树的最小数据代替要删除的结点（这里采用查找左子树最大数据来代替）\n            BiTree tempNode&#x3D;root-&gt;lchild;\n            if(tempNode-&gt;rchild!&#x3D;NULL)&#123;\n                tempNode&#x3D;tempNode-&gt;rchild;\n            &#125;\n            root-&gt;key&#x3D;tempNode-&gt;key;\n            DeleteNode(root-&gt;lchild,tempNode-&gt;key);\n        &#125;\n    &#125;\n&#125;</code></pre></li>\n</ul>\n","text":"二叉排序树的定义typedef int KeyType; typedef struct BSTNode&#123; KeyType key; struct BSTNode *lchild,*rchild; &#125;BSTNode,*BiTree; 插入操作 每次插入从根结点开...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.6k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%8E%92%E5%BA%8F%E6%A0%91%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%9A%E4%B9%89\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二叉排序树的定义</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%8F%92%E5%85%A5%E6%93%8D%E4%BD%9C\"><span class=\"toc-text\">插入操作</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2\"><span class=\"toc-text\">搜索</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%88%A0%E9%99%A4%E7%BB%93%E7%82%B9\"><span class=\"toc-text\">删除结点</span></a></li></ol>","author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juejin":"","customs":{}}},"mapped":true,"prev_post":{"title":"数据结构代码实现：顺序查找,二分查找,KMP算法","uid":"1ed24a617f1cbb7cd98bc55a230d31e9","slug":"DataStructure-KMP","date":"2020-05-18T11:57:32.000Z","updated":"2020-05-19T14:18:21.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/DataStructure-KMP.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/20200518195818.png","text":"存储结构定义#define ElemType int typedef char* SString; &#x2F;&#x2F;顺序表的定义 typedef struct &#123; ElemType *elem;&#x2F;&#x2F;数据 int TableLen;&#x2F;...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"2.3k","symbolsTime":"2 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/categories/数据结构.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"数据结构","slug":"数据结构","count":11,"path":"api/tags/数据结构.json"},{"name":"C++","slug":"C","count":11,"path":"api/tags/C.json"},{"name":"考研","slug":"考研","count":11,"path":"api/tags/考研.json"}],"author":{"name":"CHEN","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://cjpnice-picture.oss-cn-hangzhou.aliyuncs.com/img/202109161140460.jpg","link":"/","description":"学无止境","socials":{"github":"https://github.com/cjpnice","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","wechat":"","qq":"","weibo":"","zhihu":"","csdn":"","juej